<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 06:18:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国正在努力利用储能的繁荣，呼吁更多</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/china-struggling-make-use-boom-energy-storage-calls-even-more-2024-07-05/</link><description>在中国山东省的一片贫瘠的土地上，一排排看起来像薄薄的白色集装箱的东西排列在一起。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 05:42:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/china-struggling-make-use-boom-energy-storage-calls-even-more-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车电池制造商如何在储能领域脱颖而出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-chinas-ev-battery-makers-stack-up-energy-storage-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国电动汽车电池巨头CATL 300750.SZ和BYD 002594.SZ正在关注不断增长的固定储能市场。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 05:28:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-chinas-ev-battery-makers-stack-up-energy-storage-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院听取黄之锋和其他民主党人的减刑请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-court-hears-mitigation-pleas-joshua-wong-other-democrats-2024-07-05/</link><description>著名香港活动家黄之锋的律师周五表示，黄之锋应被视为涉及 47 名民主党人的具有里程碑意义的颠覆案件的积极参与者，但他敦促法院因他提前认罪而从轻判刑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 04:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-court-hears-mitigation-pleas-joshua-wong-other-democrats-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大为批准关键矿产的大型并购交易设定了很高的标准</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/canada-sets-high-bar-approving-large-ma-deals-critical-minerals-2024-07-05/</link><description>加拿大周四向采矿业发出通知，任何针对该国关键矿产生产商的重大交易只有在“最特殊的情况下”才会获得批准。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 03:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/canada-sets-high-bar-approving-large-ma-deals-critical-minerals-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报告中国更多军事活动，呼吁缓和局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-more-chinese-military-activity-calls-de-escalation-2024-07-05/</link><description>台湾周五报道称，中国在附近重新进行了军事活动，并进行了另一次“战斗巡逻”，政府呼吁北京在扣押一艘台湾渔船后不要加剧紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 03:45:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-more-chinese-military-activity-calls-de-escalation-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>随着电动汽车关税生效，中国公布了欧盟白兰地调查的下一步措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-take-talks-seriously-ev-tariffs-go-into-effect-2024-07-05/</link><description>中国周五宣布对欧洲白兰地进口进行反倾销调查的下一步，在欧盟委员会对中国制造的电动汽车临时关税生效的同一天，紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:22:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-eu-take-talks-seriously-ev-tariffs-go-into-effect-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市创历史新高；工党压倒性胜利后英镑平静</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-05/</link><description>亚洲股市周五创下新高，因投资者预计美国 9 月份降息，情绪乐观，而欧元在法国大选前触及三周高点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:18:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>美元在非农就业数据公布前大幅下跌；英镑大获全胜英国大选</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-three-week-lows-pound-takes-uk-election-stride-2024-07-05/</link><description>周五，在可能影响利率前景的非农就业数据公布之前，美元处于近三周低点附近的守势，而英镑则坚挺，因为工党有望在英国大选中赢得绝大多数席位。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:08:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-three-week-lows-pound-takes-uk-election-stride-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国商务部将对进口欧盟白兰地进行反倾销听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-commerce-ministry-hold-anti-dumping-hearing-eu-brandy-imports-2024-07-05/</link><description>据周五发布的声明称，中国商务部将于7月18日对原产于欧盟的进口白兰地进行反倾销听证会。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 02:03:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-commerce-ministry-hold-anti-dumping-hearing-eu-brandy-imports-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国拒绝西方在联合国会议上提出的人权改革的重要呼吁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-key-western-calls-human-rights-reforms-un-meeting-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国周四拒绝了西方主导的人权改革建议，包括要求香港和新疆维吾尔人享有更大自由的呼吁，但接受了盟友的其他建议，试图在联合国会议上捍卫自己的记录。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 17:38:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-key-western-calls-human-rights-reforms-un-meeting-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟公布了中国电动汽车关税计算</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-lays-out-its-china-ev-tariff-calculations-2024-07-04/</link><description>欧盟委员会周四公布了对中国电动汽车市场为期九个月的调查结果，深入了解了其计算关税的方式以及为支持其最引人注目的贸易案件而收集的证据。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-lays-out-its-china-ev-tariff-calculations-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国需求疲软削弱印度钻石出口，行业寻求支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/weak-chinese-demand-dents-indias-diamond-exports-industry-seeks-support-2024-07-04/</link><description>一家主要贸易机构负责人周四表示，由于主要市场中国的需求疲软，印度的切割和成品钻石出口一直步履蹒跚，除非政府向该行业提供支持，否则出口不太可能稳定下来。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:36:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/weak-chinese-demand-dents-indias-diamond-exports-industry-seeks-support-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>华为高管否认先进芯片短缺将阻碍中国人工智能雄心的观点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-exec-rejects-idea-that-advanced-chip-shortage-will-hamper-chinas-ai-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国科技巨头华为（HWT.UL）的一位高管周四驳斥了最先进人工智能芯片的短缺将阻碍中国成为人工智能领导者的目标的观点，但表示需要创新来解决这个问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-exec-rejects-idea-that-advanced-chip-shortage-will-hamper-chinas-ai-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟电动汽车关税决定后，名爵、蔚来暗示今年汽车价格上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mg-nio-hint-car-price-increases-this-year-following-eu-ev-tariff-decision-2024-07-04/</link><description>在欧盟决定确认对中国进口电动汽车征收关税后，中国品牌名爵和蔚来周四表示，他们可能会在今年晚些时候提高在欧洲的汽车价格。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:23:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mg-nio-hint-car-price-increases-this-year-following-eu-ev-tariff-decision-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>对欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/reaction-eu-duties-china-built-evs-2024-07-04/</link><description>欧盟将从周五起对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收高达37.6%的临时关税，这将加剧欧盟迄今为止最大贸易案中与北京的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 10:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/reaction-eu-duties-china-built-evs-2024-07-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>